The Classic III stethoscope is used by students and medical professionals alike to identify, listen to, and study heart, lung, and other body sounds for physical assessment, patient monitoring, and diagnosis. Tunable diaphragm technology—a 3M invention—lets clinicians hear different frequency sounds by simply adjusting the pressure on the chestpiece. Hold the chestpiece with light pressure to hear low frequency sounds; press a little more to hear higher frequency sounds. This time-saving feature allows the healthcare provider to focus on the patient, while the non-chill diaphragm provides patient comfort. Headset tension is easily adjusted for head size and comfort by squeezing together or pulling apart the eartubes. Snap-tight, soft-sealing eartips conform to individual ears for an excellent acoustic seal and comfortable fit. Eartips snap firmly onto the ends of the eartubes and, for safety, require a significant effort to remove. Resilient next-generation tubing retains its shape and flexibility even after folding tightly into a pocket. It provides longer stethoscope life due to improved resistance to skin oils and alcohol, and is less likely to pick up stains. Next-generation tubing is not made with natural rubber latex, a benefit to sensitive medical professionals and their patients. And, to play its part in the protection of human health and the environment, the next-generation tubing does not contain phthalate plasticizers. The Classic III stethoscope is made in the USA for consistent quality. It comes complete with large and small soft-sealing eartips, non-chill bell sleeve, and instructions.

Title: Healthbuddy Zerotox Herbal Pre Shave Oil
Description: Shaving is an integral part of men’s regular grooming rituals and calls for detailed attention and care. It makes your skin dry, rough and exposes your skin to many dermal problems like itching, irritation, razor bumps, burns, inflammations and even ingrown hair issues over time. Healthbuddy Zerotox brings you an easy pre-shave conditioning system that hydrates your whiskers for a comfortable and smooth close shave with minimal or no irritation. Healthbuddy Zerotox Handmade Pre Shave Oil is a lightweight and natural lubricating oil fortified with the goodness of Almond, Jojoba, Eucalyptus and Rosemary. Over and above that being a presentation by the Zerotox brand, the oil comes free of any added toxins like SLS and Paraben. It contains no alcohol or mineral oil and is vegan without any animal component. Furthermore, the oil has skin-smoothening properties and balances skin oil production too. On application it makes your skin super-soft and works as a natural antiseptic with great medicinal and healing effects. Its mild aroma does not get heady and synchronizes well with your favourite shaving cream, soap, aftershave or cologne. The oil renders a protective lubrication layer between your delicate facial skin and the sharp edge of the razor, therefore reducing the skin irritation that often occurs as a result of shaving. By softening the stubble, it allows the razor to move smoothly. To properly apply this pre shave oil, rinse your face thoroughly with warm water and apply a few drops of oil to the palm of your hand. Rub your palms together and gently massage the oil onto your face across the entire shaving area with equal coverage of the oil. Let the oil set on your skin for at least a minute. Apply your soap or cream lather to your face and proceed to shave as normal.
